---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy - Sliding Puzzle Solver"
  description="Privacy Policy for the Sliding Puzzle Solver website and how we handle user data."
  canonical="https://sliding-puzzle-solver.com/privacy-en"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl">
        <span class="block text-primary">Privacy Policy</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-gray-500">
        How we collect, use, and protect your personal information
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Information Collection</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          When you use Sliding Puzzle Solver, we may collect the following types of information:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700">
          <li><strong>Automatically Collected Information:</strong> Including IP address, browser type, access time, page browsing records, and other technical information</li>
          <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> We use the browser's localStorage to save your puzzle state and preference settings</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics Data:</strong> Anonymous usage statistics collected through tools like Google Analytics</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Information Use</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          The information we collect is used for the following purposes:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700">
          <li>Providing and maintaining our services</li>
          <li>Improving user experience and website functionality</li>
          <li>Analyzing website usage and performance</li>
          <li>Ensuring website security and preventing abuse</li>
          <li>Complying with legal requirements</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Cookies and Similar Technologies</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We use cookies and similar technologies to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700">
          <li>Save your puzzle game state and settings</li>
          <li>Remember your preference settings</li>
          <li>Analyze website traffic and usage patterns</li>
          <li>Provide personalized user experience</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings, but please note that disabling cookies may affect the normal functionality of the website.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Information Sharing</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We will not sell, rent, or otherwise disclose your personal information to third parties, except in the following circumstances:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700">
          <li>With your explicit consent</li>
          <li>Required by law or government departments</li>
          <li>To protect our rights, property, or safety</li>
          <li>In cooperation with trusted third-party service providers (such as Google Analytics), but only as necessary to provide services</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Data Security</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We take reasonable technical and administrative measures to protect your information security:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700">
          <li>Using HTTPS encryption for data transmission</li>
          <li>Regularly updating security measures</li>
          <li>Limiting employee access to personal information</li>
          <li>Monitoring and preventing unauthorized access</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Data Retention</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We only retain your information for as long as necessary:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700">
          <li>Locally stored data is managed by your browser and can be cleared at any time</li>
          <li>Server logs are typically retained for 30-90 days</li>
          <li>Analytics data is processed according to Google Analytics retention policies</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. Your Rights</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          You have the following rights regarding your personal information:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700">
          <li>Access and understand the information we collect about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your personal information</li>
          <li>Object to or restrict certain data processing activities</li>
          <li>Clear local storage data in your browser at any time</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">8. Third-Party Links</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external websites and recommend that you review their privacy policies.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">9. Children's Privacy</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Our service is directed to the general public and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we discover that we have collected personal information from children, we will delete it immediately.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">10. Policy Updates</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. For significant changes, we will post a notice on the website. Continued use of the service indicates your acceptance of the updated policy.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">11. Contact Us</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          If you have any questions about this privacy policy or need to exercise your rights, please contact us through the following means:
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Email: <a href="mailto:support@sliding-puzzle-solver.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">support@sliding-puzzle-solver.com</a>
        </p>

        <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
            Last Updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US')}
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout> 